{"tid":2204432,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《閃電俠》電影將重啟DC電影宇宙！","createTime":"2020-09-16T05:04:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-20T11:18:02.000Z","uid":28114,"like":7,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"9c1d57b012120bffdd69a54a75384708f4005b06","tid":2204432,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T05:04:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://geek-base.toy-people.com/?p=9919&amp;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgeek-base.toy-people.com%2F%3Fp%3D9919%26&d=%2F2JumwqaKkMO2nYek6mTvfY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=ee71d91f\" target=\"_blank\">https://geek-base.toy-people.com/?p=9919&amp;</a>"},{"pid":"e58d54b402afa2cd7fd5b9ef783fcba7d2aca977","tid":2204432,"uid":164163,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T05:05:24.000Z","msg":"正 DC又贏marvel<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42fc995f8710bbc084840021a8bbe4fb118ed01d","tid":2204432,"uid":28114,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T05:06:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/geekbase/160000813665.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fgeekbase%2F160000813665.jpg&h=2ec60209&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nDC FanDome活動的第二天的重點項目之一為《閃電俠》電影，在該電影中我們將看到伊薩‧米勒（Ezra Miller）以閃電俠（Scarlet Speedster）的身份活耀著。雖然我們已經知道了這部電影的一些細節，那就是班‧艾佛列克（Ben Affleck）和麥克‧基頓（Michael Keaton）所飾演的的蝙蝠俠將回歸演出。<br />\n<br />\n▼芭芭拉&middot;馬希提<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/geekbase/16000081233.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fgeekbase%2F16000081233.jpg&h=b5c87ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而電影監製芭芭拉&middot;馬希提（Barbara Muschietti）在這次的DC FanDome的粉絲問答中還透露出一些令人振奮的消息。<br />\n<br />\n她說：「好吧！我希望影迷親自去電影院看這部電影，所以我不會透露太多情報。」「不過我會說本作將會非常有趣，而且將會有許多DC的角色出現，而閃電俠會是這部電影的核心角色。他負責串起這些角色和時間線。而這部電影更會重啟DC宇宙！它不僅會帶來全新的內容，更不會將之前發生的一切拋棄。」<br />\n<br />\n▼ 安迪&middot;馬希提<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/geekbase/160000826394.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fgeekbase%2F160000826394.jpg&h=dd3578b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n導演安迪&middot;馬希提（Andy Muschietti）在上個月在接受採訪時說：「從某種意義上講，這部電影具有一定的連結性，它暗示了有一個統一的宇宙，在這個宇宙中，我們之前所見過的所有電影都是有關聯性的。」「也就是說您所看過的一切皆存在，同時也和你接下來要看到的一切都存在於同一個多元宇宙中。」<br />\n<br />\n▼他們是兄妹喔！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/geekbase/160000842791.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fgeekbase%2F160000842791.jpg&h=c3da00cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n安迪&middot;馬希提接著說：「讓我著迷的是在《閃電俠》中的情感戲。」「這部戲的情感戲使得電影變得有趣。我不保證本片會有任何恐怖元素（他是《牠》（IT）系列的導演），但這片會是一部擁有偉大情操的超級英雄電影。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/geekbase/160000847256.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fgeekbase%2F160000847256.jpg&h=b8559dc7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這部電影據說受到DC那著名的漫畫大事件《閃點》（Flashpoint）的啟發。《閃電俠》預計在2022年6月2日正式上映。"},{"pid":"a60fde2c56003e7237bd76da39c8b8ae89991b20","tid":2204432,"uid":28114,"like":15,"dislike":5,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T05:07:16.000Z","msg":"又reboot，屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d9718f9e7a99d6224b1a4a383516ff2ad4ed6e3","tid":2204432,"uid":175896,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T05:09:10.000Z","msg":"雖然我們已經知道了這部電影的一些細節，那就是班‧艾佛列克（Ben Affleck）和麥克‧基頓（Michael Keaton）所飾演的的蝙蝠俠將回歸演出。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n即係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0476247be1c09fd1abe1aa0b2137e1ac15f143a8","tid":2204432,"uid":97080,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T05:09:13.000Z","msg":"電腦咩<br />\n成日reboot"},{"pid":"e31cdcb7bf14f2cc6e33e9ebfc353ef489572ea0","tid":220